					  <h1 class="card-title text-white">Canteens</h1>
					  <h5 class="card-text text-white">To munch food at midnight</h5>
					  <p>
						Canteen, a place students run to treat themselves for a job done well, to socialize, or when bored or 
						when mess food is unbearable to the core. NITT provides a ton of canteen options, so you will never 
