						Restaurants, a place of special dining where students go after enjoying a day out 
						or after buying components for mini-projects :) To know more click below to see 
						reviews of other students and if free to leave a review of your own!
					  </p>
					  <a href="/Restaurants">
						<button class="btn btn-transparent btn-outline-light rounded-3">Review Restaurants</button>
					  </a>
					</div>
